import numpy as np

def calc_diss_energy_fd(tau, strs):
    delta_tau = np.diff(tau)
    delta_strs = np.diff(strs)
    diss_energy = np.abs(0.5 * delta_strs / delta_tau)
    total_diss_energy = np.sum(diss_energy)
    return total_diss_energy
